room_title: Escape room "Rivalry Week" by Escape109 in Charlotte
room_description: We have beaten our rivals, the Main Street Howlers, the last three years and we expect the same this year. With the big game coming up, some of the Main Street students thought they could distract us by stealing our championship ring. We will see who has the last laugh. We have an hour to get back what they have taken before the school opens and we are busted. While we are at it, let's see if we can get something of theirs too.
